te und ihre weltweiten Verbindungen intensivierte.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 4aFrancke, Gotthilf August. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aButterweck, Christel, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMüller, Thomas, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aWessel, Carola, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Literary and Cultural Studies - 1990 - 1999z9783110637830oZDB-23-GLC0 cprintz978348484200740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311094938440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110949384423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110949384/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GLCc1990d1999